The bottom layer is a soft, flexible vinyl with a special removable adhesive that is easily positioned, applied without air bubbles. Next we print the bottom layer with UV protected, fade resistant inks that deliver superb photo quality designs in vibrant colors. Finally we bond a professional grade laminate over the entire skin adding a glossy protective finish.
